  "2026-07-06T23:57:34.994Z",claude-code-agent,"Implementation note: live duplicate/dependency checks found pm-rjqr remains the canonical query/read SDK item; blockers pm-lodl and pm-muhw are closed. Bundling pm-395t because it touches src/sdk/runtime.ts and the same SDK dogfood surface. Planned files: src/cli/register-list-query.ts, src/cli/register-operations.ts, src/sdk/runtime.ts, tests/unit/sdk/sdk-index.spec.ts, docs/SDK.md."
  "2026-07-07T00:22:10.657Z",claude-code-agent,"Implementation bundle update: expanding PR scope per user direction to combine pm-rjqr, pm-395t, pm-98cz, pm-25d0, and pm-qfte. Current code routes CLI read/query commands through public SDK read primitives, keeps structured PmClient.run('create', ...) support, removes inline imports from touched registration modules, and adds lifecycle SDK primitive wrappers plus tests."
  "2026-07-07T00:56:14.623Z",codex-sdk-primitives-agent,"Evidence: public SDK read primitives and lifecycle bundle verified. Full coverage passed at 2026-07-07T00:54Z with 264 files, 5447 tests, and 100/100/100/100 coverage. Also passed pnpm typecheck, pnpm lint, pnpm security:scan, pnpm audit --audit-level moderate, pm health --check-only --summary --json, and installed-package dogfood from npm pack in /tmp. GitHub check: open dependabot PRs #465/#462/#461 remain separate; #461 has pre-existing failing CI. Auto-release latest scheduled run on 2026-07-06 succeeded and npm/GitHub latest is 2026.7.6."
  "2026-07-07T01:14:53.153Z",codex-sdk-primitives-agent,"Follow-up evidence after pre-push Greptile review: defaulted SDK create/update mutation option parameters, preserved SDK author precedence over lifecycle assignee aliases, and added regression coverage for no-options update plus assignee fallback behavior. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/sdk/sdk-index.spec.ts; pnpm typecheck; pnpm lint; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (Statements 100%, Branches 100%, Functions 100%, Lines 100%; 5448 tests)."
  "2026-07-07T01:29:23.811Z",codex-sdk-primitives-agent,"Pre-push review follow-up: Greptile review d8627c63-d12f-4c7d-a1d1-2eb565d52de0 reported no review comments. Addressed its summary consistency note by defaulting the standalone SDK create wrapper options to {} as well. Fresh verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/sdk/sdk-index.spec.ts; pnpm typecheck; pnpm lint; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (5448 tests, Statements/Branches/Functions/Lines all 100%)."
